1. File Upload System
    - Upload multiple files simultaneously.
    - Each file is uploaded in a separate thread.
    - Improves user experience and performance.
    - Simulates parallel I/O-bound operations.

2. Email Notification System
    - Send email after user registration or purchase.
    - Main thread handles registration.
    - Background thread sends email.
    - Keeps UI responsive and decouples tasks.

3. Background Logging System
    - Logs important events (e.g., user actions).
    - Log tasks are submitted to a thread or thread pool.
    - Main application is not delayed by file/database I/O.
    - Ensures smooth and uninterrupted user operations.